OL,3,CSenior parish official resigns after
OL,4,Cfailing to submit accounts
OL,6,FSt Peter Port's Senior Constable has
OL,7,Fresigned after admitting she has
OL,8,F"fallen short" by failing to submit
OL,9,Fthe Douzaine's annual accounts for the
OL,10,Fpast three years.
OL,12,FZoe Lihou says that high staff
OL,13,Fturnover and a difficult recruitment
OL,14,Fprocess means the Parish's audited
OL,15,Faccounts have not been presented since
OL,16,F2021.
OL,18,FShe adds the role has made her feel
OL,19,F"stretched" and cited personal reasons
OL,20,Ffor her decision to step down on
OL,21,FFriday 9 August.
