OL,3,CSenior parish official resigns after
OL,4,Cfailing to submit accounts
OL,6,FJunior Constable, Diane Mitchell, will
OL,7,Ftake up the position of Senior
OL,8,FConstable.
OL,10,FMs Lihou says: "There's rightfully so
OL,11,Fmuch responsibility and accountability
OL,12,Fof Douzainiers but we are all just
OL,13,Fvolunteers.
OL,15,F"I felt like my personal life was
OL,16,Fbeing sidelined due to the amount of
OL,17,Fwork I had to do and I just couldn't
OL,18,Fcope."
OL,20,FShe adds: "I fully accept I have not
OL,21,Ffulfilled what I need to do.
