OL,3,CSenior parish official resigns after
OL,4,Cfailing to submit accounts
OL,6,F"If I carried on in post, it would
OL,7,Fhave not been fair on me or the
OL,8,FDouzaine."
OL,10,FThere are laws in place that require
OL,11,FConstables to publish audited
OL,12,Ffinancial statements for parishes with
OL,13,Fan income of more than #250,000 - this
OL,14,Fwould include St Peter Port.
OL,16,FAccording to Ms Lihou, the Parish
OL,17,Ffinances have not been in a position
OL,18,Fwhere they could be audited since 2020.
OL,20,FShe explains: "The auditors cannot
OL,21,Faudit what's not there.
