OL,3,CSenior parish official resigns after
OL,4,Cfailing to submit accounts
OL,6,F"It's a really unfortunate position to
OL,7,Fbe in. I really care about the
OL,8,FDouzaine and there was numerous
OL,9,Ffactors as to why the finances weren't
OL,10,Fin place to be audited but I fully
OL,11,Faccept it's my responsibility.
OL,13,F"However, I have full confidence that
OL,14,FDiane will do a great job. She will
OL,15,Fhave a great team around her."
OL,17,FITV News understands the Douzaine will
OL,18,Fmeet on Tuesday night (13 August) to
OL,19,Fdiscuss the matter further.
